Description: kinto-megaphone
        ===============
        
        |travis| |master-coverage|
        
        .. |travis| image:: https://travis-ci.org/glasserc/kinto-megaphone.svg?branch=master
            :target: https://travis-ci.org/glasserc/kinto-megaphone
        
        .. |master-coverage| image::
